OL,5,G2000 Some Mothers Do 'Ave 'Em
OL,6,     FThe Hospital Visit: Frank
OL,7,     Fstruggles while Betty is in
OL,8,     Fhospital, blowing himself up with
OL,9,     Fa steak and kidney pudding, but
OL,10,     Fthe fun really starts when he
OL,11,     Fvisits Betty in the ward.
OL,12,G2040 Some Mothers Do 'Ave 'Em
OL,13,     FThe Psychiatrist: Michael Crawford
OL,14,     Fin the classic comedy. Convinced
OL,15,     Fhe is a failure, Frank visits a
OL,16,     Fpsychiatrist. By the end of his
OL,17,     Fstory, the doctor can only agree.
