OL,5,G0100 Flipping Bangers
OL,6,     FSaab 99: Gus and Will seek a
OL,7,     FScandinavian car and settle on a
OL,8,     FSaab. They'd prefer a classic 99,
OL,9,     Fbut can only find an older 99 that
OL,10,     Fwas bought for a rally but can't
OL,11,     Fgo the distance.
OL,12,G0200 Flipping Bangers
OL,13,     FRover: Gus and Will set out to buy
OL,14,     Fa Honda-based Rover 800 coupe. At
OL,15,     Fonly 650 pounds it seems too good
OL,16,     Fto be true - and when they turn
OL,17,     Fup, they aren't sure whether to
OL,18,     Fproceed.
